		<lb n="16" break="no"/>yilukku pāṇṭi
		<lb n="17" break="no"/>maṇṭalattu matu
		<lb n="18" break="no"/>rai Utaiya-vaḷa n
		<lb n="19" break="no"/>āṭṭu Aḷaṟṟūr nā
		<lb n="20" break="no"/>ṭṭu kuḷattūr-āṉa
